The RP2040-Tiny_ is a :bbl:`mini sized` RP2040 development board.
With a splitted board design, USB and keypad circuits can be separated
and connected over a FPC cable and an adapter PCB in a flexible manner.
The castellated module allows soldering direct to carrier boards.

