       .. rst-class:: rst-columns

       - Dual core Arm Cortex-M0+ processor running up to 133㎒
       - :bbk:`264㎅` on-chip SRAM
       - :bbk:`2㎆` on-board QSPI flash with XIP capabilities
       - USB 1.1 controller (host/device)
       - Adapting USB-C port via :bbk:`adapter board`
       - On-board :bbl:`FPC 8-pin connector` to adaptor board
       - On-board :bbl:`RGB LED`
       - On-board :bbl:`3.3V LDO regulator with 500㎃`
       - Adapting :bbl:`RESET` button via :bbk:`adapter board`
       - Adapting :bbl:`BOOT` button via :bbk:`adapter board`
       - :bbl:`20 GPIO` pins via :bbk:`edge pinout`
       - :bbk:`2 UART` peripherals
       - :bbk:`2 I2C` controllers
       - :bbk:`2 SPI` controllers
       - :bbk:`16 PWM` channels
       - :bbl:`4 ADC` analog inputs
       - 8 Programmable I/O (PIO) state machines for custom peripherals
       - 1 Watchdog timer peripheral
       - 1 Temperature sensor on-chip

